title: Demi Lovato's Sexy, Action-Packed "Confident" Video Is Here
text:
Demi Lovato's much-anticipated "Confident" video has FINALLY arrived. The singer released it exclusively on Marriott Rewards earlier this morning, and it's as fearless and badass as the trailers would have had you believe . ​Watch as she gets hauled into prison, makes her great escape, and then teams up with Michelle Rodriguez to take down a couple of sniveling jerks in suits. And o bviously, this being a Robert Rodriguez-directed video, there's a lot of black leather, literal ass-kicking, and Demi and Michelle both ride off into the sunset on their motorcycles at the end, all while Demi sings, "What's wrong with being confident?" Absolutely nothing, Demi.
